(2496, 1, '2015-09-23 07:35:45', '2015-09-23 07:35:45', '<h1>About TradeHero</h1>\r\n<p>Our vision at TradeHero is to democratise the world of investing through disruptive knowledge sharing. We believe everyone can learn to invest when you combine the power of crowdsourced intelligence with a fun, intuitive, and non-threatening platform. That’s why we’ve developed a gamified virtual investment network using real world data that makes it easy to learn by doing, share real time insights, and compete to win real cash, making it that much more fun to learn!</p>\r\n<p>We’re a sandbox grooming the capital markets investors of tomorrow, while triggering ideas for the investors of today.</p>\r\n<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\n<p>TradeHero is built by former wall street trading platform geeks, mobile gaming gurus from Electronic Arts, and seasoned startup athletes.</p>\r\n<div class="row members">\r\n	<div class="column small-four">\r\n[th_member name="Dinesh Bhatia"\r\nphoto="/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Dinesh.jpg"\r\nposition="CEO and Co-founder"\r\nlinkedin="http://www.linkedin.com/in/dineshbhatia"]\r\n<p>Seasoned entrepreneur and ex-Entrepreneur-In-Residence &amp; Venture Partner with Vickers Venture Capital.</p>\r\n[/th_member]\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="column small-four">\r\n[th_member name="Dominic Morris"\r\nphoto="/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/bio-dom.jpg"\r\nposition="CTO and Co-founder"\r\nlinkedin="http://sg.linkedin.com/in/dam99"]\r\n<p>Ex-Microsoft Consulting and Standard Chartered/Citibank responsible for global equities technology deployment strategy.</p>\r\n[/th_member]\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class="column small-four small-last">\r\n[th_member name="Jeff Tang"\r\nphoto="/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Jeff.jpg"\r\nposition="President-China &amp; SVP-Global"\r\nlinkedin="http://cn.linkedin.com/in/jefftang75/"]\r\n<p>Ex-China Head of netMobile AG &amp; WAZAP, extensive mobile APP/games background.</p>\r\n[/th_member]\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Investors</h2>\r\n<p>MyHero is